Class Piston

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.midlocanics.frc.gongaware.part.Piston

  • public class Piston
extends java.lang.Object
    A representation of a piston. This is used as a convenience for operating two solenoids in tandem.
    Author:
    Ross Gongaware
